National Clandestine Laboratory Register Map for Colorado 

The U.S. Department of Justice provides this data as a public service. It contains addresses of some locations where law enforcement agencies reported they found chemicals or other items that indicated the presence of either clandestine drug laboratories or dumpsites. Please see the DEA website for a conditions of use statement.
